dergirds the massive amounts of money that companies like Meta or Google sp=
end on R&D; =E2=80=9Cbuild once run anywhere=E2=80=9D is a dominant model w=
hen =E2=80=9Canywhere=E2=80=9D is the entire world (ex-China, anyways).

Rulings like this, though, do continue chipping away at that model. To that=
