oulders; it=E2=80=99s just a cost of doing business at this point, and pres=
umed to be a one-time expense. I=E2=80=99m not sure that=E2=80=99s entirely=
 correct, though: decisions like this do have long-term impacts on the fund=
amental economics of big tech.

That noted, the reaction ($META is actually up today) does seem justified i=
n this case: this decision ought to redouble efforts for the U.S. and E.U. =
to come to an agreement on data transfer, which won=E2=80=99t erase this fi=
ne but should address the possibility of similar rulings against other tech=
